Name: Description
Unemployment Rate: Individuals 16 years and older actively seeking employment (within the last four weeks) who are unemployed.

Name: Source Notes
Unemployment Rate: U.S. Census Bureau, American Community Survey 1-Year Estimates, Table C23001 (2005-2013), Table S2301 (2014-2019);  retrieved from https://data.census.gov/.

Name: Notes
Unemployment Rate: The unemployment rates reported here are different than the official unemployment rates reported quarterly by the U.S. Bureau of Labor Statistics.
